data.description: Welcome to Oak Ridge Estates! Located within walking distance to Lake LBJ, this stunning 3 bedroom, 3 full bathroom home is a rare find. With no carpet – only luxury vinyl plank flooring and tile throughout – you won't have to worry about cleaning or maintenance. This open concept house features granite countertops, recessed lighting, and integrated blinds for an easy clean look. The exterior has been freshly painted exterior (2023). Enjoy outdoor living with a covered patio and green egg grill that conveys with the house. You'll also have plenty of parking space onsite with carport and extra parking area available - perfect for visitors or those weekend projects! There's also an amazing studio in the back which could be used as a workshop, art studio or even a she shed! The real bonus of this property is just down the street - access to the boat ramp as part of the Oak Ridge Estates community clubhouse. Take advantage of all that lake life has to offer while staying within 15 minutes of Marble Falls city centre. Don't miss out on this great opportunity - houses don't come up often in this neighborhood! Boat and side by side are negotiable too - so contact us today before it's gone forever!
